549  void BeginCG() {
550  App( "CGPROGRAM" );
551 
552  if( dependencies.tessellation ) {
553  App( "#pragma hull hull" );
554  App( "#pragma domain domain" );
555  App( "#pragma vertex tessvert" );
556  } else {
557  App( "#pragma vertex vert" );
558  }
559  App( "#pragma fragment frag" );
560 
561 
562 
563  switch( currentPass ) {
564  case PassType.FwdBase:
565  App( "#define UNITY_PASS_FORWARDBASE" );
566  break;
567  case PassType.FwdAdd:
568  App( "#define UNITY_PASS_FORWARDADD" );
569  break;
570  case PassType.Deferred:
571  App( "#define UNITY_PASS_DEFERRED" );
572  break;
573  case PassType.ShadCast:
574  App( "#define UNITY_PASS_SHADOWCASTER" );
575  break;
576  case PassType.Meta:
577  App( "#define UNITY_PASS_META 1" );
578  break;
579  }
580 
581 
582  if( LightmappedAndLit() ) {
583  App( "#define SHOULD_SAMPLE_SH ( defined (LIGHTMAP_OFF) && defined(DYNAMICLIGHTMAP_OFF) )" );
584 
585  }
586 
587  if(ps.catLighting.reflectprobed ){
588  App ("#define _GLOSSYENV 1");
589  }
590 
591 
592  if( ps.catGeometry.showPixelSnap )
593  App( "#pragma multi_compile _ PIXELSNAP_ON" );
594 
595 
596  App( "#include \"UnityCG.cginc\"" );
597 
598  if( ShouldUseLightMacros() )
599  App( "#include \"AutoLight.cginc\"" );
600  if( IncludeLightingCginc() )
601  App( "#include \"Lighting.cginc\"" );
602  if( dependencies.tessellation )
603  App( "#include \"Tessellation.cginc\"" );
604  if( IncludeUnity5BRDF() ){
605  App( "#include \"UnityPBSLighting.cginc\"" );
606  App( "#include \"UnityStandardBRDF.cginc\"" );
607  }
608  if( currentPass == PassType.Meta ) {
609  App("#include \"UnityMetaPass.cginc\"");
610  }
611  if( ps.catMeta.cgIncludes.Count > 0 ) { // Custom CG includes
612  for (int i = 0; i < ps.catMeta.cgIncludes.Count; i++){
613  string incStr = ps.catMeta.cgIncludes[i];
614  if( incStr == string.Empty )
615  continue;
616  App( "#include \"" + incStr + ".cginc\"" );
617  }
618  }
619 
620  if( currentPass == PassType.FwdBase ) {
621  App( "#pragma multi_compile_fwdbase" + ps.catBlending.GetShadowPragmaIfUsed() );
622  } else if( currentPass == PassType.FwdAdd ) {
623  App( "#pragma multi_compile_fwdadd" + ps.catBlending.GetShadowPragmaIfUsed() );
624  } else {
625  App( "#pragma fragmentoption ARB_precision_hint_fastest" );
626  if(!ps.catExperimental.forceNoShadowPass)
627  App( "#pragma multi_compile_shadowcaster" );
628  }
629 
630  if( currentPass == PassType.Deferred ) {
631  App( "#pragma multi_compile ___ UNITY_HDR_ON" );

637  App( "#pragma multi_compile DYNAMICLIGHTMAP_OFF DYNAMICLIGHTMAP_ON" );
638  }
639 
640  if( UseUnity5Fog() )
641  App( "#pragma multi_compile_fog" );
642 
643 
644 
645 
646  List<int> groups = new List<int>();

649  string[] mcPrags = n.TryGetMultiCompilePragmas( out group );
650  if( !groups.Contains( group ) && mcPrags != null ) {
651  groups.Add( group );
652  for( int i = 0; i < mcPrags.Length; i++ ) {
653  App( "#pragma multi_compile " + mcPrags[i] );

655  }

657  //if(n.IsProperty() && n.property is SFP_Branch){

659  //}
660  }
661 
662 
663 
664  if( dependencies.DoesIncludePlatforms() )
665  App( "#pragma only_renderers " + dependencies.GetIncludedPlatforms() );
666  if( dependencies.IsTargetingAboveDefault() ) {
667  if( ps.catExperimental.force2point0 )
668  App( "#pragma target 2.0" );

670  App( "#pragma target " + dependencies.GetShaderTarget() );

696  void PassTags() {

714  bool ip = ps.catBlending.ignoreProjector;
715  bool doesOffset = ps.catBlending.queuePreset != Queue.Geometry || ps.catBlending.queueOffset != 0;
716  bool hasRenderType = ps.catBlending.renderType != RenderType.None;
717  bool hasBatchConfig = ps.catMeta.batchingMode != SFPSC_Meta.BatchingMode.Enabled;
718  bool hasAtlasConfig = ps.catMeta.canUseSpriteAtlas;
719  bool hasPreviewType = ps.catMeta.previewType != SFPSC_Meta.Inspector3DPreviewType.Sphere;
720 
721  if( !ip && !doesOffset && !hasRenderType && !hasBatchConfig && !hasAtlasConfig && !hasPreviewType )
722  return; // No tags!
723 
724  BeginTags();
725  if( ip )
726  AppTag( "IgnoreProjector", "True" );
727  if( doesOffset ) {
728  string bse = ps.catBlending.queuePreset.ToString();
729  string ofs = "";
730  if( ps.catBlending.queueOffset != 0 )
731  ofs = ps.catBlending.queueOffset > 0 ? ( "+" + ps.catBlending.queueOffset ) : ( ps.catBlending.queueOffset.ToString() );
732  AppTag( "Queue", ( bse + ofs ).ToString() );
733  }
734  if( hasRenderType )
735  AppTag( "RenderType", ps.catBlending.renderType.ToString() );
736  if( hasBatchConfig ) {
737  if(ps.catMeta.batchingMode == SFPSC_Meta.BatchingMode.Disabled)
738  AppTag( "DisableBatching", "True" );
739  if(ps.catMeta.batchingMode == SFPSC_Meta.BatchingMode.DisableDuringLODFade)
740  AppTag( "DisableBatching", "LODFading" );
741  }
742  if( hasAtlasConfig ) {
743  AppTag( "CanUseSpriteAtlas", "True" );
744  }
745  if( hasPreviewType ) {
746  if( ps.catMeta.previewType == SFPSC_Meta.Inspector3DPreviewType.Plane)
747  AppTag( "PreviewType", "Plane" );
748  if( ps.catMeta.previewType == SFPSC_Meta.Inspector3DPreviewType.Skybox )
749  AppTag( "PreviewType", "Skybox" );
750  }
751 
752 
753 
754  End();

1265  void CalcGloss() {
1266  AppDebug( "Gloss" );
1267  if( ps.catLighting.glossRoughMode == SFPSC_Lighting.GlossRoughMode.Roughness ){
1268  App( "float gloss = 1.0 - " + ps.n_gloss + "; // Convert roughness to gloss" );
1269  if( Unity5PBL() )
1270  App( "float perceptualRoughness = " + ps.n_gloss + ";" );
1271  } else {
1272  App( "float gloss = " + ps.n_gloss + ";" );
1273  if( Unity5PBL() )
1274  App( "float perceptualRoughness = 1.0 - " + ps.n_gloss + ";" );
1275  }
1276 
1277  if( Unity5PBL() ) {
1278  if( ps.catLighting.geometricAntiAliasing ) {
1279  App( "float3 spaaDx = ddx(i.normalDir);" );
1280  App( "float3 spaaDy = ddy(i.normalDir);" );
1281  App( "float geoRoughFactor = pow(saturate(max(dot(spaaDx,spaaDx),dot(spaaDy,spaaDy))),0.333);" );
1282  App( "perceptualRoughness = max(perceptualRoughness, geoRoughFactor);" );
1283  }
1284  App( "float roughness = perceptualRoughness * perceptualRoughness;" );
1285  }
1286 
1287  if( !InDeferredPass() ) {

2047  string SumString( bool[] bools, string[] strings, string defStr ) {
2048 
2049  int validCount = 0;
2050  for( int i = 0; i < bools.Length; i++ ) {
2051  if( bools[i] )
2052  validCount++;
2053  }
2054 
2055  if( validCount == 0 )
2056  return defStr;
2057 
2058  string s = "";
2059  int added = 0;
2060  for( int i = 0; i < strings.Length; i++ ) {
2061  if( bools[i] ) {
2062  s += strings[i];
2063  added++;
2064  if( added < validCount )
2065  s += " + ";
2066  }
2067  }
2068  return s;
2069  }
